</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>iFixit 成為 Steam Deck 指定零件銷售商　提供官方授權維修服務</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/17/ifixit-valve-steam-deck/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=ifixit-valve-steam-deck</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 17 Feb 2022 09:01:58 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[ifixit]]></category><category><![CDATA[steam deck]]></category><category><![CDATA[Valve]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086665</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Valve 將於約一星期後便會推出 Steam Deck，近日便宣布將出售 Steam Deck 官方零件，並 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Valve 將於約一星期後便會推出 Steam Deck，近日便宣布將出售 Steam Deck 官方零件，並由 iFixit 擔任官方授權零件銷售商並提供維修服務。</p><p>Valve 宣布將公開於售 Steam Deck 官方零件，供用家自行修理。而 iFixit 將成為 Valve 旗下 Steam Deck 及 Valve Index VR 的首個官方授權零件銷售商，除了銷售 Valve 零件外，亦會提供維修服務。不過 Valve 未有表明會於 iFixit 出售哪款零件，細節詳情有待稍後公布。</p><p>iFixit 早前曾上網拆解 Steam Deck 的影片，更稱過程容易，僅需十字螺絲批便可將整個 Steam Deck 拆解，給其可修復性高達 7 分。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.43.08.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.43.08-694x360.png" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.43.08-694x360.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.43.08-1280x663.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.43.08-768x398.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.43.08-1536x796.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.43.08-2048x1061.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.43.08.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： iFixit</p><p>影片指出只需取出 Steam Deck 背面的 8 個螺絲便能把背殼拆開，更建議觀眾把背殼與機身分拆時以膠片扳開。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.33.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.33-694x360.png" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.33-694x360.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.33-1280x663.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.33-768x398.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.33-1536x796.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.33-2048x1061.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.33.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.58.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086670" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.58-694x360.png" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.58-694x360.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.58-1280x663.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.58-768x398.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.58-1536x796.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.58-2048x1061.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.42.58.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： iFixit</p><p>把背殼拆開後便能看到電池連接線，只需將連接線向外拉便能將其移除。Steam Deck 電池以 L 字型設計，並由兩塊組成，規格為 40.04 Wh、5313 mAh，電池續航力可高達 8 小時。Steam Deck 內的電池黏得十分緊，影片中的解說員指更換電池為維修 Steam Deck 的致命弱點，需使用扁平的刮削工具反覆削鏟粘合劑方可移除電池。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.14.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.14-694x372.png" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.14-694x372.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.14-1280x685.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.14-768x411.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.14-1536x822.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.14-2048x1097.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.14.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.20.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.20-694x372.png" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.20-694x372.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.20-1280x685.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.20-768x411.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.20-1536x822.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.20-2048x1097.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.45.20.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： iFixit</p><p>移除 Steam Deck 的 SSD 也十分方便，只需把旁邊的螺絲拆出便可。iFixit 指 Steam Deck 的可修復性高且多元，只需一顆螺絲和滑套式 EMI 防護罩便可更換 SSD。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.44.53.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.44.53-694x372.png" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.44.53-694x372.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.44.53-1280x685.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.44.53-768x411.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.44.53-1536x822.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.44.53-2048x1097.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 4.44.53.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： iFixit</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_97673"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4T0RZ6ustKQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/platform/amp/2022/2/15/22935171/valve-steam-deck-replacement-parts-teardown-ifixit">The Verge</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
